Rule: Age Factor: Increasing age can lead to a positive outcome.
Marital Status: Being married is associated with a positive outcome.
Education Level: Higher education levels such as a Doctorate can lead to a positive income outcome.
Gender: Gender can play a role in the income prediction.
Occupation: Moving to a different occupation, such as Professional, can lead to a positive outcome.
Hours Per Week: Increasing the number of hours worked per week can lead to a positive income outcome.
